                </div>
            </center>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <center>
                <a href="../Home/GetInvolved"><img src="../Images/vol.png" style="width:150px; height:150px; " /></a>
            </center>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <center>
                <!--Paypal API-->
                <form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_top">
                    <input name="cmd" value="_s-xclick" type="hidden">
                    <input name="hosted_button_id" value="PJCBKP6NDWHTL" type="hidden">
                    <input src="../Images/donate.png" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!" type="image" border="0"
                           style="width:150px; height:150px;">
                </form>
            </center>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Objectives:</h2>
            <p> 1.	All students graduate college and career ready. <br /><br />
                2.	All students in Mentoring & Enrichment program have increased exposure to college and career options. <br /><br />
                3.	All students in After School Tutoring program meet JCPS district standards for their grade in reading, English, and math. <br /><br />
                4.	Students in After School Tutoring programs will improve unsatisfactory grades to position themselves for acceptance into top high schools in the county. <br /><br />
                5.	Students in After School Tutoring programs will improve communication skills through weekly group discussions and writing prompts. <br /><br />
                6.	Students will have positive views of their future and achievements. <br /><br />
                7.	Students will set and work toward high educational, personal, and career goals. <br /><br />
                8.	Students in the Mentoring & Enrichment program will understand the value of service learning and of giving back to the community. <br /><br />
                9.	Students in our Mentoring & Enrichment program will have a richer understanding of both their own and other cultures. <br /><br />
                10.	Ambassadors will have increased leadership opportunities both within our programs and in the Louisville community. <br /><br />
</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h2>Our Mission and Vision</h2>
        <p>
            Adelante Hispanic Achievers’ mission is to inspire and empower Hispanic/Latino youth and their families to become self-sufficient, successful individuals who have the tools they need to achieve their dreams and participate as creative, educated world citizens.
            <br /><br />
            Our goals are to guide Hispanic youth as they set and meet high educational, personal, and career goals and to surround each student with a network of supportive, informed adults including parents, mentors, tutors, community leaders, and other positive role-models.
        </p>
        <center>
<br /><br />
            <h2>Check out our Sponsors!</h2>
            <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" style="width: 300px; height: 175px; margin: 0 auto">
